"""
1c. Use curl to retrieve only the device information for a single device (ID=2 for example). 
Once again this will require authorization. The API URL for this would be (assuming ID 2):

https://netbox.lasthop.io/api/dcim/devices/2/
"""



curl -H "Authorization: Token $NETBOX_TOKEN" https://netbox.lasthop.io/api/dcim/devices/2/ --insecure | jq
